      "title": "Myanmar's state of emergency will be extended for another 6 months",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Myanmar's National Security and Defense Council decided on Sunday to extend Myanmar's state of emergency for another six months.",
        "The council said that this decision was taken for the necessary preparations for the multi-party general elections."
      ],
